articles.author: Andrew Webster
articles.title: The Witcher continues on Netflix with the Sirens of the Deep animated movie - The Verge
articles.description: At its Geeked Week event, Netflix announced a brand-new spinoff called The Witcher: Sirens of the Deep, an animated movie that will once again star Geralt of Rivia.
